- Fully rewrote PluginManager; moved filesystem ops to a separate class; made all functions lock-protected

- Added JavaScript runtime support for third-party plugins
- Implemented all functions in PluginInterface to work with external functions
- Added more attributes (e.g. developer)
- Added function to check codeName
- Added safety to both init and dispose

- Added `fromMap` to all universal formats
- Set all mandatory fields as non-nullable

- Updated xhamster scraping to new JSON maps; fixed `PreviewVideos` scraping reliability
- Fix `progressThumbnail` position not updating immediately on drag start

- Added share and open-in-browser to video fly-out menu
- Improved `OptionsSwitch` util (generic leading icon)

- Fixed settings not saving correctly
- Reset DB due to schema changes; simplified update/continuity path; added upgrade step

- disabled Google's encrypted dependency metadata blob for android
- Updated official plugin codenames

